column1: Baby Barnaby's////OMG!!! The green eggs and ham are off the heezy fo sheezy my neezy!!! My first time there and I was pleased! Who would've thought that eggs
column2: spinach and artichoke hearts would make an oh so delicious combination! Our waiter (I feel bad I forgot his name) was so nice and courteous. I can't forget to mention the biscuits and that scrumdiddlyumptious chicken apple sausage! FOODGASM!!!!!!! I will definitely become a regular here!
